text:
Attending a church event there
Good

Very nice church. The decorations is beautiful and the surroundings was clean. Some event were also held in here. Like weddings for example. There are also a pantry big enough for people to sit and eat.

If you are looking for a community to journey in life together with Jesus we welcome you to visit on sunday. Our services start at 10.30am (English, Chinese and Teochew). Also do consider enrolling your children at Newton kindergarden which is well known for its bilingual (English & Chinese) syllabus.
Join us! Good food after service, two pokestops with a gym beside.
Very friendly and welcoming church with good facilities.
